B. Allen, Berkeley: University of California Press, 1975.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, <em>De sole</em>, first published, together
with Ficino&rsquo;s <em>De lumine</em>, Florence: Antonio di
Bartolommeo Miscomini, 1496. Italian translation: Marsilio Ficino,
<em>Scritti sull&rsquo; astrologia</em>, tr. Ornella Pompeo Faracovi,
Milan: Biblioteca Universale Rizzoli, 1999.</li>

<li>Franckenberg, Abraham von, <em>Oculus sidereus</em>, Gdansk: Georg
Rheten, 1644.</li>

<li>Galilei, Galileo, <em>Sidereus Nuncius</em>, Venice: Tommaso
